rows.label: tlk42350146_03_msg0003
rows.name:
It's natural to be surprised,
mo. Hototo was so surprised
I almost fainted, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350146_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Mo-mo-mo?! I'm too late in
finding out, mo? He passed
away a long time ago, mo?!

rows.label: tlk42350146_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Hototo is always cooped up
in this cave, so I'm out of
touch with the world... mo.
